{"tid":1501981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"玩blackbloc 不如玩blackwater ，反正香港人鍾意捐錢，有無得諗","createTime":"2019-08-24T14:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T16:28:31.000Z","uid":264388,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9d8949dcb1d8c6cac534c6ab36685a66eac92084","tid":1501981,"uid":264388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:09:40.000Z","msg":"先豐服務<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%85%88%E8%B1%90%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2F%25E5%2585%2588%25E8%25B1%2590%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=26f096ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E5%85%88%E8%B1%90%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99</a><br />\n<br />\n【拆局】上市港企主理「一帶一路」安保 招攬美國黑水創辦人加盟<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B3/213723/%E6%8B%86%E5%B1%80-%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%BB%E7%90%86-%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E5%AE%89%E4%BF%9D-%E6%8B%9B%E6%94%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%BB%91%E6%B0%B4%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25BB%25B3%2F213723%2F%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E5%25B8%2582%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BC%2581%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E7%2590%2586-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25B8%25B6%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25B7%25AF-%25E5%25AE%2589%25E4%25BF%259D-%25E6%258B%259B%25E6%2594%25AC%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%25BB%2591%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E5%2589%25B5%25E8%25BE%25A6%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%258A%25A0%25E7%259B%259F&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=19dc5206\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E8%AD%B0%E4%BA%8B%E5%BB%B3/213723/%E6%8B%86%E5%B1%80-%E4%B8%8A%E5%B8%82%E6%B8%AF%E4%BC%81%E4%B8%BB%E7%90%86-%E4%B8%80%E5%B8%B6%E4%B8%80%E8%B7%AF-%E5%AE%89%E4%BF%9D-%E6%8B%9B%E6%94%AC%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E9%BB%91%E6%B0%B4%E5%89%B5%E8%BE%A6%E4%BA%BA%E5%8A%A0%E7%9B%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不過都要睇佢地係咪真係認錢唔認人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n黑水創辦人擬雇兵推動委內瑞拉變天<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bannedbook.org/bnews/zh-tw/baitai/20190502/1122099.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bannedbook.org%2Fbnews%2Fzh-tw%2Fbaitai%2F20190502%2F1122099.html&d=mYJIHVlKms%2F2btm24%2BMsOvDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=d1e70f73\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bannedbook.org/bnews/zh-tw/baitai/20190502/1122099.html</a><br />\n路透社周二引述4名消息人士報道，美國私人保安公司黑水國際（Blackwater）創辦人普林斯（Erik Prince）正推動一項計劃，擬集資協助反對派領袖招募5000雇傭兵前往委內瑞拉，協助推翻總統馬杜羅。白宮及委國對立陣營均拒絕評論報道。有專家擔心有關做法恐觸發內戰。<br />\n<br />\n集資3億元 招5000雇傭兵<br />\n<br />\n消息人士稱，普林斯計劃以瓜伊多的名義在哥倫比亞等拉美國家招請4000至5000名雇傭兵，以到委國作戰及穩定局勢。他認為，瓜伊多已獲國際承認，有權自行組建軍隊，由拉美地區人士組成的雇傭兵政治上會容易為人接受。他亦尋求向私人投資者集資4000萬美元（約3.1億港元），亦期望取用因製裁措施被各國政府凍結的委國資產作為行動資金。<br />\n<br />\n白宮國家安全委員會發言人馬奎斯（Garrett Marquis）拒絕評論；瓜伊多發言人則稱，未曾與普林斯討論任何行動，但拒絕回應進一步提問。部分美國及委國的保安專家認為，有關計劃在政治上太牽強，且有觸發內戰的潛在風險。<br />\n<br />\n普林斯長年推動「戰爭民營化「，曾派雇傭兵赴中亞、非洲與中東地區的戰亂地區，屢惹爭議。2007年，黑水國際派駐伊拉克、為國務院人員提供保安服務的雇傭兵涉在巴格達射殺17名平民，觸發國際震怒，4名涉事者分別被控謀殺及誤殺罪成。2010年，普林斯出售黑水國際后，近年再開設專售軍火的黑水美國（Blackwater USA），2014年又在香港開設涉及保安及保險業務的先豐服務集團。（路透社）"},{"pid":"e0caf0ee13337f24fce266c906700e65864c2c87","tid":1501981,"uid":30138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:10:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f944911161e632529bbbc7912860269ce32c57f","tid":1501981,"uid":264388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:11:12.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"19b8954314c0827b4b0e3a550435e2735637a3fc","tid":1501981,"uid":264388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:11:24.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"2c5522d8ba87985adfe0540255764f3a33c0a602","tid":1501981,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T14:11:40.000Z","msg":"想支持<br